className.description: Additional classes added to the overflow tab

defaultTitleText.description: The text which displays when an overflowing tab isn't selected

focusTimeoutDelay.description: Time in ms to wait before firing the toggles' focus event. Defaults to 0

overflowingTabs.description: The tabs that should be displayed in the menu (Type: TabProps[])

shouldPreventScrollOnItemFocus.description: Flag indicating if scroll on focus of the first menu item should occur.

showTabCount.description: Flag which shows the count of overflowing tabs when enabled

toggleAriaLabel.description: The aria label applied to the button which toggles the tab overflow menu
